{"tid":265601,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"原本以本土為名義好地地，黃藍絲都要join本土","createTime":"2017-05-31T18:03:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T02:07:40.000Z","uid":90221,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be72f75ac28e3e35e6cb7950f462b1027a37d8e9","tid":265601,"uid":90221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/12901538_964878973597723_7905307752920207889_o_IWoPm_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F12901538_964878973597723_7905307752920207889_o_IWoPm_1200x0.png&h=20d48cb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://scontent.cdninstagram.com/t51.2885-15/s480x480/e15/11379775_1482823252009665_1490836605_n.jpg?ig_cache_key=MTAwNzcxMTA0ODkxMzExNDY4NQ%3D%3D.2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscontent.cdninstagram.com%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fs480x480%2Fe15%2F11379775_1482823252009665_1490836605_n.jpg%3Fig_cache_key%3DMTAwNzcxMTA0ODkxMzExNDY4NQ%253D%253D.2&h=1e34bb90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知689推廣港獨<br />\n<br />\n引晒D小學雞<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjswfCa15rUAhULn5QKHZeYDh8QjRwIBw&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fm3.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6621983%26type%3DBW&amp;psig=AFQjCNGF6il792iD9Iqt5GYxQaHomdkYJQ&amp;ust=1496338968218297\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Di%26rct%3Dj%26q%3D%26esrc%3Ds%26source%3Dimages%26cd%3D%26cad%3Drja%26uact%3D8%26ved%3D0ahUKEwjswfCa15rUAhULn5QKHZeYDh8QjRwIBw%26url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fm3.hkgolden.com%252Fview.aspx%253Fmessage%253D6621983%2526type%253DBW%26psig%3DAFQjCNGF6il792iD9Iqt5GYxQaHomdkYJQ%26ust%3D1496338968218297&h=1222ad6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即刻搞到本土派收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無人否定你港獨立場既價值<br />\n<br />\n問題係你用咩理論說服人 <br />\n<br />\n日日開post唔係宣傳立場論述，以文鬥文<br />\n講野無point，仲走去join埋花生台D大話精行賤格路線<br />\n網絡係追求真相既自由領域<br />\n<br />\n靠無腦無底蘊既空頭口號做召來，<br />\n引來既都只會係班無腦無基礎既群眾<br />\n<br />\n以為拆熱血城邦台就即刻有10萬民眾靠寵港獨？<br />\n<br />\n唔好發夢啦，本土派個pool好細架咋<br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.wp.com/tmhk.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/image1.jpg?fit=1280%2C960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Ftmhk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fimage1.jpg%3Ffit%3D1280%252C960&h=80536655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我buy港獨都唔會投靠本民青政哩兩堆小學雞"},{"pid":"26bc0128619bfe24cbef9c0ae875ed111602209a","tid":265601,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:16:15.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"e12eaaa66be9bf63f6bcbbe67a9e6ef62313ee61","tid":265601,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d43cf6aad7362bb41a507a46101d11798ea66fc6","tid":265601,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T22:50:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛狗出沒注意！ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會員：9527~  <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 編號：48157</span></span><br />\n五毛狗 （9527~ #48157）  <ins>同 雜種有親「習大大」+ 打<em><strong>殘體字</strong></em>， 係連登傳播中共語言</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tg8us6vx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftg8us6vx&h=2fc572aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五毛狗 （9527~ #48157）<ins>公然<em><strong>抹黑</strong></em>支持香港獨立嘅人</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/t04bvcg9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.